name: Beauty
description: The artist we are going to introduce today was born in Ukraine, a small town of Krivoy Rog.  He name is Marka Akatieva and despite her young age of 19 years old she has a huge audience in her social networks of more than 100k followers on Instagram and on TikTok.  She studied for 8 years at an art school and now she is engaged in self-study, constantly practicing, and planning to get specialized education in Europe.
